    "content": "On the nature of the stock market: Simulations and experiments Blok\r(2000)\rBlok, \rH.\r \r(2000).\r \rOn the nature of the stock market: Simulations and experiments (Departmental defense).\r Retrieved from \rhttps://www.cs.ubc.ca/~rikblok/research/presented/blok00/index.html\rDownload",
